POST-INSTALL:
		* copy dillorc in your "~/.dillo" directory.

INFO:
		* By default, dillo disable all cookies. See
		http://www.dillo.org/Cookies.txt
		for more informations

PATCHES: 
                * http://www.hyperborea.org/software/dillo/modified.html
                * character-set localization patches:
                  http://bobuk.ipost.ru/packages/dillo/index.html
                * frames and tabbed browsing:
                  http://www.geocities.com/ikbenfrank/
                * collection of many small changes:
	          http://www.hyperborea.org/software/dillo/modified.html
                * scale down a page:
                  http://pigeond.net/dillo/

